<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">A Dangerous Hate Campaign Is Ramping Up Against Ilhan Omar</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media"><div class="mediawrapper"><iframe src="https://www.democracynow.org/embed/story/2019/4/16/rep_ilhan_omar_faces_death_threats" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div></figure></div>
