</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Despite threats to the congresswoman&#8217;s safety, Trump continued &#8220;using her as fodder for ridicule&#8221; in a weekend speech.</div>
