<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/mike-pence-smears-ilhan-omar-in-aipac-speech-did-he-just-prove-her-point/">Mike Pence Smears Ilhan Omar in AIPAC Speech: Did He Just Prove Her Point?</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Pence is trying to win Jewish votes by attacking Democrats on Israel &#8212; but he&#8217;s very unlikely to succeed.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/sophia-tesfaye/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Sophia Tesfaye</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.salon.com/2019/03/26/mike-pence-smears-ilhan-omar-in-aipac-speech-did-he-just-prove-her-point/' itemprop='url'>Salon</a></span></dd>
</dl>
